{
  "id": "69b8657d97825bbba940a34b",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:お前だって論法",
  "created": 1773692318,
  "updated": 1773692332,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b8657d97825bbba940a34b",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:お前だって論法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692318,
      "updated": 1773692318
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659e0000000000d1c7c5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692318,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7c6",
      "text": "はーい、今日のゆるトークのテーマは「[お前だって論法]」だよ～！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7c7",
      "text": "ネットだと「お前もやってるじゃんｗ」みたいなやつね。英語だと Whataboutism とか言われたりするらしい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7c8",
      "text": "ゲームのチャットとかSNSでもめっちゃ見るんだよね～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7c9",
      "text": "「お前それ言うけど、お前も前に同じことしてたじゃん」ってやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ca",
      "text": "りか的にはこれ、どういうジャンルのやつなん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7cc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7cd",
      "text": "論理学では[** 誤謬（ごびゅう）]の一種。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ce",
      "text": "具体的には「トゥ・クォークエ（tu quoque）」と呼ばれる。ラテン語で「お前もだ」という意味。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7cf",
      "text": "構造は単純。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d0",
      "text": " AがBを批判する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d1",
      "text": " Bが「でもAも同じことをしている」と言う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d2",
      "text": " 批判そのものの正しさを検討せず、論点をずらす",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d3",
      "text": "つまり論点のすり替えだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d4",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d5",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tu_quoque",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d6",
      "text": "要点：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d7",
      "text": " 相手の主張の真偽ではなく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d8",
      "text": " 相手の人格や過去の行動に焦点を移す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7d9",
      "text": "これで議論が停止する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7db",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7dc",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7dd",
      "text": "たしかに日常の会話でも、よく見かけますわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7de",
      "text": "たとえば――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7df",
      "text": "「遅刻はよくありませんよ」と誰かが注意したとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e0",
      "text": "「でもあなたもこの前遅れていましたよね」と返すような。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e1",
      "text": "それは……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e2",
      "text": "注意の内容が正しいかどうかではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e3",
      "text": "注意した人の過去へと話を逸らしてしまっていますのね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e4",
      "text": "（小さく微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e5",
      "text": "人は責められると、つい自分を守ろうとしてしまうもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e6",
      "text": "その気持ち自体は、少しだけ分かる気もいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7e9",
      "text": "あーそれそれ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ea",
      "text": "まさにSNSのコメント欄って感じｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7eb",
      "text": "例えばさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ec",
      "text": "「このゲーム会社バグ多すぎ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ed",
      "text": "って言ったら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ee",
      "text": "「でもお前○○社のときは擁護してたよな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ef",
      "text": "みたいな返信くるやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f0",
      "text": "いや、今のバグの話してんだけど！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f1",
      "text": "ってなるやつね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f4",
      "text": "典型例だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f5",
      "text": "議論として整理すると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f6",
      "text": " 命題A：このゲーム会社にはバグが多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f7",
      "text": " 反論B：あなたは別の会社のバグを批判しなかった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f8",
      "text": "BはAの真偽を否定していない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7f9",
      "text": "だから論理的には反論になっていない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7fa",
      "text": "これをソフトウェアのレビューに例えると分かりやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7fb",
      "text": "仮にコードレビューで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7fc",
      "text": "「この関数はメモリリークの可能性があります」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7fd",
      "text": "と言われたとする。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7fe",
      "text": "そこで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c7ff",
      "text": "「でも君も前のコードでミスしてたよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c800",
      "text": "と言っても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c801",
      "text": "メモリリークの問題は消えない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c802",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c803",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c804",
      "text": "あーーー",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c805",
      "text": "それめっちゃ分かりやすいｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c806",
      "text": "バグはバグだもんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c807",
      "text": "「お前もバグ出してた」って言われても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c808",
      "text": "今のバグ直せよって話だし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c809",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80b",
      "text": "ただ……少しだけ、別の見方もできる気がします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80c",
      "text": "もしも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80d",
      "text": "「自分は絶対に正しい人間です」という顔で",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80e",
      "text": "厳しく誰かを責めている方がいたなら――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c80f",
      "text": "その方の過去の振る舞いを思い出して、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c810",
      "text": "「あなたも同じことをしていましたよ」と",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c811",
      "text": "伝えたくなる気持ちも……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c812",
      "text": "人として、なくはない気がいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c813",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c814",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c815",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c816",
      "text": "それは重要な視点。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c817",
      "text": "実は「お前だって論法」が出る背景には、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c818",
      "text": "二つのケースがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c819",
      "text": " 1. 単なる論点ずらし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81a",
      "text": "  議論に負けそうなので話題を逸らす。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81b",
      "text": " 2. 偽善の指摘",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81c",
      "text": "  相手のダブルスタンダードを問題にする。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81d",
      "text": "2. の場合は、完全に無意味とは言えない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81e",
      "text": "ただし、それでも元の問題の真偽とは別。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c81f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c820",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c821",
      "text": "なるほど！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c822",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c823",
      "text": " 「お前もやってる！」 → 話そらしになること多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c824",
      "text": " 「その基準ダブスタじゃね？」 → ルールの話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c825",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c826",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c827",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c828",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c829",
      "text": "要点整理：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82a",
      "text": " 1. 主張の正しさ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82b",
      "text": " 2. 発言者の一貫性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82c",
      "text": "この二つは別問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82d",
      "text": "議論では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82e",
      "text": "まず 1（主張の正しさ） を検討するべき。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c82f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c830",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c831",
      "text": "なんだか……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c832",
      "text": "人の会話というのは、鏡のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c833",
      "text": "相手の言葉の中に、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c834",
      "text": "自分の過去や弱さが映ってしまうと――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c835",
      "text": "つい目をそらしたくなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c836",
      "text": "そして「あなたもでしょう」と",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c837",
      "text": "鏡を相手に向けてしまうのかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c838",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c839",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83b",
      "text": "うわ、詩人モードきたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83c",
      "text": "でも確かにさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83d",
      "text": "ネットってレスバ勝ちたいモードになるから、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83e",
      "text": "論点ずらしがめっちゃ増える気がする。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c83f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c840",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c841",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c842",
      "text": "研究でも、オンライン議論は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c843",
      "text": "論理よりアイデンティティ防衛が強く働くと言われている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c844",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c845",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Whataboutism",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c846",
      "text": "簡潔に言うと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c847",
      "text": " 批判された",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c848",
      "text": " 自分の陣営を守りたい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c849",
      "text": " 相手の矛盾を探す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84a",
      "text": "この流れで「お前だって」が発動する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84d",
      "text": "じゃあさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84e",
      "text": "もし言われたらどう返すのがいいんだろ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c84f",
      "text": "「いやそれ今関係なくね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c850",
      "text": "って言うしかない？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c851",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c852",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c853",
      "text": "比較的有効なのはこの形。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c854",
      "text": "論点を戻す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c855",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c856",
      "text": "「その点は別として、今の問題は〇〇です」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c857",
      "text": "英語圏でもよく使われる対応。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c858",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c859",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85a",
      "text": "それは、とても穏やかでよろしい言い方ですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85b",
      "text": "誰かを恥ずかしめるのではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85c",
      "text": "ただ静かに話題を元へ戻す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85d",
      "text": "議論というのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85e",
      "text": "勝ち負けではなく――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c85f",
      "text": "少しずつ真実に近づく旅のようなものですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c860",
      "text": "（やさしく微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c861",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c862",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c863",
      "text": "今日のまとめいくよ～！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c864",
      "text": "ふーこ的まとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c865",
      "text": " 「お前だって論法」＝ 話そらしが多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c866",
      "text": " でもたまに ダブスタ指摘もある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c867",
      "text": " 言われたら 論点戻すのが安定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c868",
      "text": "つまり…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c869",
      "text": "レスバよりバグ修正しろ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86a",
      "text": "ってことだねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86d",
      "text": "技術者として、その結論には全面同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c86f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c870",
      "text": "ええ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c871",
      "text": "まずは目の前の問題を、静かに見つめること。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c872",
      "text": "それが一番大切なのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c873",
      "text": "（やわらかく微笑む）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
      "updated": 1773692320
    },
    {
      "id": "69b8659f0000000000d1c874",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773692320,
